  lines:
  - text: "Ugh\u2026 Did I fall asleep\u2026?"
  - text: "What time is it\u2026? 12 AM?!"
  - text: "Oh no\u2026 the library must have closed by now\u2026  "
  - text: "I\u2019d better get out of here before I get in trouble\u2026"
  - text: I heard rumors about an anteater roaming around... That's probably a myth
      made up by the seniors...
  - text: ...Right...?
